@startuml class_diagram_history

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam classFontSize 13
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam ClassBorderColor #555555
skinparam ClassBackgroundColor #FAFAFA

title History of Operations — Class Structure

package "src/history.py" {

    class OperationRecord << (F,lightblue) frozen dataclass >> {
        + timestamp : float
        + operation : str
        + operands : list
        + result : Any
    }

    class OperationHistory {
        - _records : list[OperationRecord]
        + __init__()
        + append(operation: str, operands: list, result: Any) : None
        + get_all() : list[OperationRecord]
        + clear() : None
        + __len__() : int
    }

}

class Calculator << src/calculator.py >> {
    - _history : OperationHistory
    + __init__()
    + add(a, b) : Numeric
    + subtract(a, b) : Numeric
    + multiply(a, b) : Numeric
    + divide(a, b) : Numeric
    + factorial(n) : int
    + square(x) : Numeric
    + cube(x) : Numeric
    + square_root(x) : float
    + cube_root(x) : float
    + power(base, exp) : Numeric
    + natural_log(x) : float
    + log_base_10(x) : float
}

class CalculatorREPL << src/input_handler.py >> {
    - _calculator : Calculator
    - _parser : ExpressionParser
    - _validator : InputValidator
    - _retry_config : RetryConfig
    + __init__(calculator: Calculator, retry_config: RetryConfig = None)
    + run() : None
    - _evaluate(raw_input: str) : str
    - _dispatch(operation: str, operands: list) : Numeric
}

class CLIHandler << src/cli.py >> {
    - _expression : str
    - _calculator : Calculator
    - _parser : ExpressionParser
    - _validator : InputValidator
    + __init__(expression: str)
    + run() : int
    - _dispatch(operation: str, operands: list) : Numeric
}

note right of OperationRecord
  Immutable value object.
  Created inside OperationHistory.append()
  using time.time() for timestamp.
end note

note bottom of CalculatorREPL
  _evaluate() calls
  _calculator._history.append()
  only on successful dispatch.
end note

note bottom of CLIHandler
  run() calls
  _calculator._history.append()
  only on successful dispatch.
end note

Calculator *-- OperationHistory : _history (1:1)
OperationHistory o-- OperationRecord : _records (1:*)

CalculatorREPL o-- Calculator : _calculator (passed in)
CLIHandler *-- Calculator : _calculator (composes)

CalculatorREPL ..> OperationHistory : appends via _calculator._history
CLIHandler ..> OperationHistory : appends via _calculator._history

@enduml
